data.title: TD Newmarket Music Series
data.text:
Newmarket Music Series presented by TD Bank Group through the TD Ready Commitment

Date: Thursdays from July 4 to August 22, 2024.

Location: Riverwalk Commons (200 Doug Duncan Drive)

Time: 6 to 9 p.m.

Join us every Thursday evening from July 4 to August 22, 2024 for a free tribute band concert at Riverwalk Commons. Each concert will feature amazing local performers and a premier tribute band.

Service Disruption: The Mercedes-Benz Newmarket Water Feature will be closing at 3:00 p.m. each Thursday in preperation for that evening's concert.

Road Closure: Timothy Street, from Doug Duncan Drive to Cedar Street, will be closed each Thursday in preperation for that evening's concert.

Thursday, July 4

The Carpet Frogs (playing the best of Classic Rock)

Opening: Freedom Train

Food and Beverage: Mulberry's Oven & Old Flame Brewing Co.

Thursday, July 11 - Canadian Rock Night

Practically Hip (a tribute to The Tragically Hip)

Summer of 69 (a tribute to Bryan Adams)

Opening:Jagged (a tribute to Alanis Morissette)

Food and Beverage: North Newmarket Lions BBQ & Market Brewing Company

Thursday, July 18

Taylor Swift Night (featuring The Beresfords)

Opening: Buck Twenty

Food and Beverage: Mulberry's Oven & Old Flame Brewing Co.

Friendship Bracelets: Help support the Newmarket Food Pantry and bring a non-perishable food item to donate. The first 1,000 individuals to donate a minimum of one (1) food item will recieve one (1) free frienship bracelet. Donations can be dropped off at one (1) of two (2) Town of Newmarket tents on site.

NOTE: Friendship bracelets will be distributed on a first come - first serve basis and are only while quantities last.

Click here to see what is currently the most needed items at the Newmarket Food Pantry

Thursday, July 25

Sweet Soul Music (featuring George St. Kitts)

Opening: Taylor Made Band

Food and Beverage: North Newmarket Lions BBQ & Market Brewing Company

Thursday, August 1

Exodus (a tribute to Bob Marley)

Opening: Ainsworth & Degrandis

Food and Beverage: Mulberry's Oven & Old Flame Brewing Co.

Thursday, August 8

Desire (a tribute to U2)

Opening: Honey Jack

Food and Beverage: North Newmarket Lions BBQ & Market Brewing Company

Thursday, August 15

Epic Eagles (a tribute to the Eagles)

Opening: The Focklers

Food and Beverage: Mulberry's Oven & Old Flame Brewing Co.

Thursday, August 22

Dwayne Gretzky

Opening: Murray Drive

Food and Beverage: North Newmarket Lions BBQ & Market Brewing Company

Be sure to check out the FREE Mercedes-Benz Newmarket Backstage Lounge every Thursday during our Newmarket Music Series presented by TD Bank Group through the TD Ready Commitment concerts. All guests are welcome to come enjoy:

Viewing the concert from our large backstage LED screen.

Lounge in a complimentary Mercedes-Benz Newmarket Muskoka chair (while availability lasts). Guests are also welcome to bring their own lawn chair and place within the Backstage Lounge as they wish.

Hang out under one of the multiple Mercedes-Benz Newmarket umbrellas.

Check out an impressive Mercedes-Benz Newmarket vechile on site.

Learn more about the Mercedes-Benz Newmarket Giveaway Contest and how you can enter with a chance to win various prizes.

Hope to see you all there!

Check out our video from the 2023 Newmarket Music Series presented by TD Bank Group through the TD Ready Commitment:

Additional Information:

Bring your own lawn chair

Please arrive early to secure a spot

Parking will be limited due to volume. Click here to view a downtown Newmarket parking map

Guests are welcome to bring non-perishable food items to donate to the Newmarket Food Pantry. Newmarket Food Pantry donation bins will be located at the Town of Newmarket booth at Riverwalk Commons.

For up-to-date weather and/or cancellation details of Town-run events please visit newmarket.ca/events or seach Town of Newmarket Events and click on the event of interest.
